    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Attaching silk chiffon or other fine, transparent material to one or both sides of a sheet of paper in order to strengthen, repair, or preserve it.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
